				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2012/08/03/16686-letat-croque-mort-et-sa-sordide-paperasse?replytocom=83992#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-83992", "83992", "respond", "16686")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
